title: Darkside Of The Force (Norwegian HipHop classic)
description:
Oscar & Salvador from Kr.Sand brought in 1998 one of Norwegian HipHop\&#039;s only classics. With help from Khari Kizzo, Anarad and Whiteshadow they created a album that\&#039;s still playable and just as nice as 9 years ago.  I recomend this album to all heads, no matter where you from. 

Enjoy!
